Review_title: One of the best documentary films i've ever seen!
Review_Text:
We don't realize it but there are certain "people" that walk among us,
smart spiritual messengers that cross paths with humans and change lives
many come and go anonymous, bet several become myth.This is a story of such a "man".We don't realize it but there are certain "people" that walk among us,
